      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is priced accordingly \u2014 please read this description carefully before inquiring. The exterior has significant cosmetic damage including multiple deep scratches, paint chips, dents, and faded sections that would require substantial bodywork to address. The interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery, cracked dashboard trim, and staining throughout. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will require attention \u2014 it runs, but is not in reliable day-to-day driving shape without repairs. This listing is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or needs a parts car. There are no surprises here: what you see is what you get, and we've priced it honestly to reflect the work it needs. Sold as-is.",
